 based show animated and politically balanced. Forum fans and lovers of literature will be riveted by the insightful and amusing vignettes and behind the scenes accounts. They will get a taste of the sharp commentary from his encounters with panels of experts, and interviews with cultural and political personalities as well as writers.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aGeneral Interest. 4aLiterary Studies. 7aBIOGRAPHY & AUTOBIOGRAPHY / Literary.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080476835140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804768351423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804768351/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles